{"tid":1635183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會選舉劇本已經寫好","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:50.000Z","uid":25643,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7c5c737fbed3231ca60b6e0abaf0305b430ace","tid":1635183,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"政府：五大訴求違反基本法﹐支持者全部DQ<br />\n<br />\n香港人包圍選舉場地<br />\n<br />\n政府：因為暴徒干擾選舉﹐宣佈餘下建制派自動當選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>燃脂焚膏風險高　要令抗爭可延續</strong><br />\n第一，首先是設想如何收割現在已經垂手可得的成果。現在已經可以盡快收割的，就是十一月底的區議會選舉。建制派及政府已經蠢蠢欲動，說要把選舉押後之目的也是顯而易見。現在大家要做的，是不要為他們這個意圖提供理據。只要繼續維繫到大部份市民的支持，這一次區議會就算不能 18 區翻盤，也應該可以把建制陣營壟斷的局面較大程度的改變。如果能夠在區議會取得較佳的戰果，對於明年立法會選舉及安插社區樁腳也應該是有利的。無論我們對現制度有幾不滿，無論大家對一個合理的制度有幾渴求，在中短期而言，於體制內爭取更大的空間仍然是一個值得收割的政治成果。千萬不要因噎廢食，不要為政府押後區議會選舉提供籍口。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%87%83%E8%84%82%E7%84%9A%E8%86%8F%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E9%AB%98-%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%AF%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2587%2583%25E8%2584%2582%25E7%2584%259A%25E8%2586%258F%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E7%25BA%258C%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=f7718772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2587%2583%25E8%2584%2582%25E7%2584%259A%25E8%2586%258F%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E7%25BA%258C%2F&h=da8271ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%87%83%E8%84%82%E7%84%9A%E8%86%8F%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E9%AB%98-%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%AF%E5%BB%B6%E7%BA%8C/</a></span>"},{"pid":"4237de5fea1a0b9d06af05b1364fe4c158ac8b1e","tid":1635183,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民撳爆總行 atm 換美金保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行call loan 然後支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"26cc5bd71155f51f30980c71bc69d730bbd010ac","tid":1635183,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"政府擘撚晒面<br />\n<br />\n仲覺得會乖乖地同你玩選舉遊戲<br />\n<br />\n唔係低能就係散水撚"},{"pid":"275a67bf2f84fb54c3f55c3db657abbb119c3524","tid":1635183,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"037b1da56b2fb37b9e0f9f485d73b702638cfb21","tid":1635183,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}